Per Anand → It was CB services who did the Azure setup for Komatsu’s first app (a community dev). If you weren't involved, then it was a manual deploy (ie, triggered off-platform).  -Find community dev who set this up for Komatsu and schedule conversation with them to walk us through how they did this.- 

